<h2>A bit about <%= @show.name %></h2>

<p>While Shawna Caspi calls Toronto home, she’s spent much of the last two years on the road in support of her fourth album, <cite>Forest Fire</cite>, a collection of songs about burning things down and building them up again.</p>

<p>Shawna recently won a silver award in the Mid-Atlantic Song Contest and played at Summerfolk and the Ottawa Grassroots Festival. She’s is also a talented painter, creating (and selling) one-of-a-kind landscapes of the scenes she spots on the road.</p>


<p><%= link_to "Spend Saturday evening with #{@show.name}", @rsvp_url %>.</p>

<p><br/>Paul</p>

